EPD_Painter
===========

Original project: EPD_Painter by Tony Weston and contributors
Source: https://github.com/tonywestonuk/EPD_Painter
License: Apache License 2.0

This copy was modified for the CrossPoint/PaperPoint ESP32-S3 reader on
2026-06-20. Local changes include integration with the project HAL, removal
of unused/shutdown modules, Arduino/ESP-IDF compatibility adjustments, and
GC16 grayscale support. Modified files carry a prominent modification notice.

The GC16 waveform table in EPD_Painter_gc16_lut.h is separately attributed
and licensed under the BSD-2-Clause/FreeBSD terms in
LICENSES/BSD-2-Clause-LovyanGFX.txt.
